 et al [EMP]. This code integrates into a single                  2525 1451
 system a number of important modules and features:               2525 1451
                                                                  2525 1451
 - Spherical and deformed Optical Model including                 2525 1451
   coupled-channels (ECIS06 by J. Raynal)                         2525 1451
