   TRISTAN by H. Lenske), and MSC NVWY model                      2525 1451
 - Exciton model with angular momentum coupling                   2525 1451
   (code DEGAS by E. Betak and P. Oblozinsky) that                2525 1451
   represents a good approximation to the DSD model               2525 1451
 - Exciton model with Iwamoto-Harada cluster                      2525 1451
   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 2525 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                2525 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   2525 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                2525 1451
   discrete transitions                                           2525 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL library [RIPL]                2525 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                2525 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               2525 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 2525 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 2525 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              2525 1451
   EXFOR/CSISRS library                                           2525 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A. Trkov)                    2525 1451
